#. module: l10n_se_excise_tax
#: model_terms:ir.actions.act_window,help:l10n_se_excise_tax.action_excise_tax_type
msgid ""
"Excise Tax Types define the per-kg rate and per-unit cap\n"
"                used by weight-based excise taxes (e.g. the Swedish\n"
"                Chemical Tax). Each type can be linked to one or more\n"
"                <em>account.tax</em> records."
msgstr ""
"Punktskattetyper definierar skattesatsen per kg och taket per enhet\n"
"                som används av viktbaserade punktskatter (t.ex. den\n"
"                svenska kemikalieskatten). Varje typ kan kopplas till\n"
"                en eller flera <em>account.tax</em>-poster."

#. module: l10n_se_excise_tax
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:l10n_se_excise_tax.view_excise_tax_type_form
msgid "e.g. Electronics (High Rate)"
msgstr "t.ex. Elektronik (hög sats)"

#. module: l10n_se_excise_tax
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:l10n_se_excise_tax.view_excise_tax_type_form
msgid "Rate"
msgstr "Skattesats"

#. module: l10n_se_excise_tax
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:l10n_se_excise_tax.view_excise_tax_type_form
msgid "Cap"
msgstr "Tak"

#. module: l10n_se_excise_tax
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:l10n_se_excise_tax.view_excise_tax_type_form
msgid "How it's used:"
msgstr "Så här används det:"

#. module: l10n_se_excise_tax
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:l10n_se_excise_tax.view_excise_tax_type_form
msgid ""
"<strong>How it's used:</strong> For every product line\n"
"                        taxed with an <em>account.tax</em> of type\n"
"                        <code>Swedish Excise Tax</code> linked to this record,\n"
"                        the excise amount per unit is\n"
"                        <code>quantity × tax_rate</code>, where\n"
"                        <em>quantity</em> is the per-product field matching\n"
"                        the chosen <strong>Unit Basis</strong>:\n"
"                        <code>net_weight_excise</code> for kg, or\n"
"                        <code>excise_volume_litres</code> for liter.\n"
"                        For kg-based taxes the result is also\n"
"                        capped at <code>max_limit</code> per unit and\n"
"                        multiplied by the per-line reduction factor\n"
"                        (Kemikalieskatt's 100% / 50% / 5% rule —\n"
"                        i.e. full / half / 5 % of the rate is paid\n"
"                        for products earning a 0 / 50 / 95 % reduction)."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Så här används det:</strong> För varje produktrad som\n"
"                        beskattas med en <em>account.tax</em> av typen\n"
"                        <code>Svensk punktskatt</code> kopplad till denna post,\n"
"                        beräknas punktskatten per enhet som\n"
"                        <code>quantity × tax_rate</code>, där\n"
"                        <em>quantity</em> är det per-produkt-fält som matchar\n"
"                        vald <strong>Enhetsbas</strong>:\n"
"                        <code>net_weight_excise</code> för kg, eller\n"
"                        <code>excise_volume_litres</code> för liter.\n"
"                        För kg-baserade skatter begränsas resultatet\n"
"                        dessutom till <code>max_limit</code> per enhet och\n"
"                        multipliceras med radens reduceringsfaktor\n"
"                        (Kemikalieskattens 100 % / 50 % / 5 %-regel —\n"
"                        dvs. hel / halv / 5 % av satsen betalas\n"
"                        för produkter med 0 / 50 / 95 % reducering)."

# --------------------------------------------------------------------
# Views – account.tax inherit (excise block + Posting Setup)
# --------------------------------------------------------------------
#. module: l10n_se_excise_tax
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:l10n_se_excise_tax.view_tax_form_excise_inherit
msgid ""
"This tax is calculated from the product's excise weight\n"
"                    and the configured per-kg rate. VAT is computed on\n"
"                    (line subtotal + excise)."
msgstr ""
"Skatten beräknas utifrån produktens punktskattevikt\n"
"                    och den konfigurerade satsen per kg. Moms beräknas på\n"
"                    (radens delsumma + punktskatt)."

#. module: l10n_se_excise_tax
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:l10n_se_excise_tax.view_tax_form_excise_inherit
msgid ""
"Editing the rate or max limit here updates the\n"
"                        underlying Excise Type and therefore every tax\n"
"                        linked to it. Confirmed sales orders and posted\n"
"                        invoices are not affected — they keep the\n"
"                        amounts computed at validation time."
msgstr ""
"Att redigera skattesatsen eller maxgränsen här uppdaterar\n"
"                        den underliggande punktskattetypen och därmed\n"
"                        alla skatter som är kopplade till den. Bekräftade\n"
"                        kundorder och bokförda fakturor påverkas inte —\n"
"                        de behåller de belopp som beräknades vid\n"
"                        valideringstillfället."

#. module: l10n_se_excise_tax
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:l10n_se_excise_tax.view_tax_form_excise_inherit
msgid "Posting Setup"
msgstr "Bokföringsinställning"

#. module: l10n_se_excise_tax
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:l10n_se_excise_tax.view_tax_form_excise_inherit
msgid ""
"These values are derived from the Definition\n"
"                            tab's invoice &amp; refund repartition lines.\n"
"                            The liability account is assigned per\n"
"                            company at install time (BAS 2616 if\n"
"                            available, else 2615 / 2640 / 2980). To\n"
"                            change it, open the Definition tab and edit\n"
"                            the repartition grid directly."
msgstr ""
"Dessa värden härleds från repartitionsraderna för\n"
"                            faktura och kredit i fliken Definition.\n"
"                            Skuldkontot tilldelas per bolag vid\n"
"                            installation (BAS 2616 om det finns,\n"
"                            annars 2615 / 2640 / 2980). För att ändra\n"
"                            det, öppna fliken Definition och redigera\n"
"                            repartitionsrutnätet direkt."

