#: model:ir.actions.act_window,name:l10n_se_excise_tax.action_excise_tax_default
#: model:ir.ui.menu,name:l10n_se_excise_tax.menu_excise_tax_default
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:l10n_se_excise_tax.view_excise_tax_default_form
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:l10n_se_excise_tax.view_excise_tax_default_list
msgid "Default Excise Tax Rules"
msgstr "Standardregler för punktskatt"

#. module: l10n_se_excise_tax
#: model_terms:ir.actions.act_window,help:l10n_se_excise_tax.action_excise_tax_default
msgid "Add a default excise tax rule"
msgstr "Lägg till en standardregel för punktskatt"

#. module: l10n_se_excise_tax
#: model_terms:ir.actions.act_window,help:l10n_se_excise_tax.action_excise_tax_default
msgid ""
"Default rules tell the module which excise tax to apply to new products: "
"either to a specific Internal Category, or as a fallback for all products. "
"They include all the per-product extras, e.g. the Kemikalieskatt Reduction "
"Level (0 / 50 / 95 %), so accountants only fill the rule once and matching "
"products inherit a complete configuration."
msgstr ""
"Standardregler talar om för modulen vilken punktskatt som ska tillämpas på "
"nya produkter: antingen för en specifik intern kategori eller som "
"reservregel för alla produkter. De innehåller alla per-produkt-"
"inställningar, t.ex. Kemikalieskattens reduceringsnivå (0 / 50 / 95 %), så "
"att redovisningsekonomen bara behöver fylla i regeln en gång och matchande "
"produkter ärver en komplett konfiguration."

#. module: l10n_se_excise_tax
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:l10n_se_excise_tax.view_excise_tax_default_form
msgid "e.g. Electronics — Kemikalieskatt high rate"
msgstr "t.ex. Elektronik — Kemikalieskatt hög sats"

#. module: l10n_se_excise_tax
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:l10n_se_excise_tax.view_excise_tax_default_form
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:l10n_se_excise_tax.view_excise_tax_default_list
msgid "(All Products — fallback)"
msgstr "(Alla produkter — reserv)"

#. module: l10n_se_excise_tax
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:l10n_se_excise_tax.view_excise_tax_default_form
msgid "Scope"
msgstr "Omfattning"

#. module: l10n_se_excise_tax
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:l10n_se_excise_tax.view_excise_tax_default_form
msgid "Defaults Applied"
msgstr "Tillämpade standardvärden"

#. module: l10n_se_excise_tax
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:l10n_se_excise_tax.view_excise_tax_default_form
msgid "How rules are matched:"
msgstr "Så här matchas reglerna:"

#. module: l10n_se_excise_tax
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:l10n_se_excise_tax.view_excise_tax_default_form
msgid ""
"when a product is flagged\n"
"                        <em>Excise Taxable</em> (or its Internal Category\n"
"                        is changed) and no excise tax is configured yet,\n"
"                        the most specific rule wins:"
msgstr ""
"när en produkt markeras som\n"
"                        <em>Punktskattepliktig</em> (eller dess interna\n"
"                        kategori ändras) och ingen punktskatt är\n"
"                        konfigurerad ännu vinner den mest specifika regeln:"

#. module: l10n_se_excise_tax
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:l10n_se_excise_tax.view_excise_tax_default_form
msgid ""
"first an active rule with a matching\n"
"                                <em>Product Category</em> (lowest\n"
"                                <em>Sequence</em> wins),"
msgstr ""
"först en aktiv regel med matchande\n"
"                                <em>Produktkategori</em> (lägsta\n"
"                                <em>Ordning</em> vinner),"

#. module: l10n_se_excise_tax
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:l10n_se_excise_tax.view_excise_tax_default_form
msgid ""
"if none, an active rule with no\n"
"                                <em>Product Category</em> (the\n"
"                                <em>All Products</em> fallback)."
msgstr ""
"om ingen finns, en aktiv regel utan\n"
"                                <em>Produktkategori</em> (reservregeln\n"
"                                för <em>Alla produkter</em>)."

#. module: l10n_se_excise_tax
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:l10n_se_excise_tax.view_excise_tax_default_form
msgid ""
"The matched rule sets the product's\n"
"                        <em>Excise Tax Type</em>, adds the linked\n"
"                        <em>account.tax</em> to its Customer Taxes and,\n"
"                        when relevant, sets the per-product\n"
"                        Kemikalieskatt <em>Reduction Level</em>."
msgstr ""
"Den matchande regeln sätter produktens\n"
"                        <em>Punktskattetyp</em>, lägger till den kopplade\n"
"                        <em>account.tax</em> bland dess kundskatter och,\n"
"                        när det är relevant, sätter Kemikalieskattens\n"
"                        per-produkt-<em>Reduceringsnivå</em>."

#. module: l10n_se_excise_tax
#: model:ir.actions.server,name:l10n_se_excise_tax.action_server_apply_excise_defaults
